pages.description: I always wanted to become a Architect so I studied in Stellenbosch and passed my national and international qualifications, realizing its not what I wanted to do ,I build up experience in construction to learn a different aspect of building and thats where passion and hard work got together to become a Commercial Property Broker, not to only SELL a client a home but a investment for my clients business and hard work.
